comments: Green (LAC) and Davis (LAL) engage and disengage off ball.
Caruso (LAL) firms up and establishes himself in a screening position in Green's (LAC) path, and marginal contact occurs to his front.
Davis' (LAL) left foot steps out of bounds at the start of his dribble.
Kuzma (LAL) places his hand to Leonard's (LAC) side momentarily as he is gathering the ball but the contact is marginal.
Leonard (LAC) gathers the ball and takes two legal steps prior to going airborne. He then loses control of the ball on his own and is the first player to touch the ball after returning to the floor.
Green (LAC) makes marginal body contact with Davis (LAL) on the perimeter.
Green (LAC) makes some contact with James' (LAL) front/side after his gather, but it is marginal.
Caruso's (LAL) releases the ball prior to landing out of bounds.
George (LAC) makes marginal contact to Green's (LAL) back as he is establishing his screening position.
Green (LAC) moves parallel alongside Davis' (LAL) drive to the basket as Davis loses his balance when lowering his shoulder towards Green's leg.
Leonard (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball after Davis (LAL) trips over Green's (LAC) leg.
Davis (LAL) legally goes to the floor and does not take another step or dribble thereafter.
Leonard (LAC)  lifts his leg to kick the ball on the pass by Davis (LAL).
Green (LAC) makes marginal contact with Davis' (LAL) front during rebounding. After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of LAC ball stood.
Green (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Green's (LAL) path and does not deliver the contact.
Green (LAL) makes some contact with George's (LAC) right foot after the release of his jump shot attempt, but it is marginal.
Leonard (LAC) places his hands to Green's (LAL) side momentarily as he sets the pick and removes them.
Morris Sr. (LAC) moves laterally into James' (LAL) path and delivers contact to his side and affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to his gather.
Jackson (LAC) makes marginal contact with James' (LAL) front after James secures the rebound and is attempting the put-back.
Morris Sr. (LAC) slightly extends his arms forward into James' (LAL) front as the screen is set, but it is marginal.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact with the inside portion of Leonard's (LAC) right arm during the step back move.
James (LAL) rests his forearm on George's (LAC) front and quickly removes it as George starts his upward shooting motion.
